    Bugs
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
** Fix in Lexer:
        Add error messages when include more than one char in \'
        Fix number bound warnings (we may have errors given a very big number)

** Fix Parser:
        Express "this should be between spaces"
        Write better error messages
        Enable parsing to continue on errors
        Add the grammar rule to write `<string-literal>[<int>]>'

** Fix in configure.ac
        Use LIBRARY_VERSION when we introduce our libraries


